WhisperBack - Send a feedback in an encrypted mail
##################################################

Copyright (C) 2009 Amnesia <amnesia@boum.org>


DESCRIPTION
===========

WhisperBack is a small pyGTK application intend to provide a
user-friendly way to send a GnuPG-encrypted feedback to the amnesia
dev team.


DEPENDENCIES
============

You need the following runtime dependancies :
  - python-gtk2
  - python-pyme

In addition, you need the following build dependancies :
  - python-distutils-extra
  - txt2tags


INSTALLATION
============

WhisperBack is packaged using distutils. To install it :
  $ ./setup.py build
and then under root
  # ./setup.py install

USAGE
=====

Please see the man page
